<ul>
<li><span data-amount=3D"1">1</span>x (5lb) bag all purpose flour or bread =
flour (I use either <a href=3D"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00P6EQGW6=
/ref=3Das_li_tl?ie=3DUTF8&amp;tag=3Demilieraffa-20&amp;camp=3D1789&amp;crea=
