<li><span data-amount=3D"0.5" data-unit=3D"cup">1/2 cup</span>&nbsp;(<span =
data-amount=3D"60" data-unit=3D"g">60g</span>) whole wheat flour (I use<a h=
ref=3D"https://amzn.to/2tX1FMl" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"nofollow noopener"=
>&nbsp;KAF whole wheat)</a></li>
<li>Water, preferably warm around 85 F&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
